Ruby/GooCanvas
==============
Ruby/GooCanvas is a Ruby binding of GooCanvas.

Requirements
------------
   Ruby: http://www.ruby-lang.org/
   GooCanvas: http://live.gnome.org/GooCanvas

Install
-------
   0. install ruby-1.8.x or later and GooCanvas.
   1. ruby extconf.rb
   2. make
   3. su
   4. make install

